[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "ユリエ",
		"romanized_name": "Jurie",
		"model_path_hash": "6932496336129827816",
		"text": "あっという間にノルト州ね。\nここ、「迷いの森林」って呼ばれているらしいわ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8415011553540267009",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "ミルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Miruca",
		"model_path_hash": "6658023269359396885",
		"text": "確かに、夜だと迷いそう。\nん、あそこにいるのって……",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1034358740077913276",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "ニオ",
		"romanized_name": "Nio",
		"model_path_hash": "1882786194477430238",
		"text": "わあ、ミルカちゃんとユリエさんだ！\nこんにちは！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8735269928136797011",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "リンカ",
		"romanized_name": "Linca",
		"model_path_hash": "2320534114475787876",
		"text": "お二人とも、久しぶりですね",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "4464667044946317190",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "アーシャ",
		"romanized_name": "Ayesha",
		"model_path_hash": "7148606200211237631",
		"text": "こんな所で会うなんて、すごい偶然だね",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5225548852493309829",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "ミルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Miruca",
		"model_path_hash": "6658023269359396885",
		"text": "久しぶり。アーシャさんがいるってことは、\nみんなで薬の素材探し？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1034358740077913276",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "アーシャ",
		"romanized_name": "Ayesha",
		"model_path_hash": "7148606200211237631",
		"text": "うん。ノルト州には珍しい薬草があるから",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5225548852493309829",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "リンカ",
		"romanized_name": "Linca",
		"model_path_hash": "2320534114475787876",
		"text": "ミルカとユリエも、何かお探しですか？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "4464667044946317190",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "ユリエ",
		"romanized_name": "Jurie",
		"model_path_hash": "6932496336129827816",
		"text": "私たちは、ランターナ各地を回っているの。\n紀行文を書こうと思って",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8415011553540267009",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "アーシャ",
		"romanized_name": "Ayesha",
		"model_path_hash": "7148606200211237631",
		"text": "紀行文を……！　素敵ですね",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5225548852493309829",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "アーシャ",
		"romanized_name": "Ayesha",
		"model_path_hash": "7148606200211237631",
		"text": "もしよかったら、途中まで一緒に行きませんか？\n道も分かりにくいし、人数が多いほうが安心かなって",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5225548852493309829",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "ユリエ",
		"romanized_name": "Jurie",
		"model_path_hash": "6932496336129827816",
		"text": "ええ。向かう方向も同じみたいだし、\n私たちからもぜひお願いするわ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8415011553540267009",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "リンカ",
		"romanized_name": "Linca",
		"model_path_hash": "2320534114475787876",
		"text": "それでは、しばらく同行ということで。\n道中、何かあれば力を合わせましょう",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "4464667044946317190",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "アーシャ",
		"romanized_name": "Ayesha",
		"model_path_hash": "7148606200211237631",
		"text": "二人とも、ありがとう。\nえへへ、なんだか心強いな",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5225548852493309829",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "ユリエ",
		"romanized_name": "Jurie",
		"model_path_hash": "6932496336129827816",
		"text": "じゃ、道はアーシャたちに任せるわ。\n私たちは、後ろからついていく",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8415011553540267009",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "ニオ",
		"romanized_name": "Nio",
		"model_path_hash": "1882786194477430238",
		"text": "あ、あっちに小さな花が咲いてるよ！　\nおねーちゃん、見てみようよ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8735269928136797011",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "アーシャ",
		"romanized_name": "Ayesha",
		"model_path_hash": "7148606200211237631",
		"text": "あ、ニオ！　待って！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5225548852493309829",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "リンカ",
		"romanized_name": "Linca",
		"model_path_hash": "2320534114475787876",
		"text": "お二人とも、お待ちください！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "4464667044946317190",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "ユリエ",
		"romanized_name": "Jurie",
		"model_path_hash": "6932496336129827816",
		"text": "……こうして、出会いに任せて歩くのもいいわね",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8415011553540267009",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "ミルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Miruca",
		"model_path_hash": "6658023269359396885",
		"text": "……そうね",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1034358740077913276",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "ニオ・アルトゥール",
		"romanized_name": "Nio Altugle",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "アーシャの妹。おっとりした姉を支えるしっかり者。\n薬についての知識が豊富で、よく姉の手伝いをしている",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8735269928136797011",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "リンカ",
		"romanized_name": "Linca",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "剣士の女性。普段はマリオンの下で働いている。\n剣の腕は確かだが、戦い以外のことは苦手",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "4464667044946317190",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "アーシャ・アルトゥール",
		"romanized_name": "Ayesha Altugle",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "薬の知識が豊富な、おっとりとした錬金術士。\n王宮の薬士として、薬の素材を研究している",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5225548852493309829",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]